                                            <strong>Meal:</strong> Chocolate Milkshake <br>
                                            <strong>Restaurant:</strong> PAI <br>
                                            <strong>Address:</strong> 324 Yonge St, Toronto, Ontario
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="">
                                        <td class="content-block aligncenter">
                                             Bring This Email (on your phone or printed out) and pickup your lunch between:
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="">
                                        <td class="content-block aligncenter">
                                             12:30 pm - 12:45 pm
